name: Spectre Fleet's Modified Entosis Link Blueprint
description: This Compact variation of the standard Entosis Link was developed by the research division of the Capsuleer organization <url=showinfo:16159//99006373>Spectre Fleet</url>. <url=showinfo:16159//99006373>Spectre Fleet's</url> forces were among the earliest to research the applications of Entosis technology and were able to optimize the standard Entosis Link for lower powergrid requirements. Originally intended for internal use only, copies of the blueprint have slipped onto the black market and can now be found by those with the right underworld connections.
